snippet.title: Pocket Troops - Android Gameplay
snippet.description: Pocket Troops is a humor-filled tactical war game that offers a unique family-friendly experience where no trooper dies in battle. Step into the role of commander as you recruit, train, and equip your ideal army and fight intense, bite-sized battles.
